solomon kalushi mahlangu was born in pretoria on 10 july in 1956 .   he was the second son of martha mahlangu .   his father left him in 1962 , and from then on only saw him infrequently .   his mother was a domestic worker and took sole responsibility for his upbringing .   the kalushi film is about the nineteen-year-old hawker , from the streets of mamelodi , a ghetto township outside pretoria in south africa .   the film is based on a true story .